title: Ep216 Social Worker Crimes
description: This week, the gals discuss a particular occupation with unique challenges (and a lot of room for error). Topics include trials and errors of the past, a bunch of turtle-loving children, and a case of grandma grand larceny. Mix yourself a mug of Kahlua and coffee, never trust a sweepstakes win, and tune in for Social Worker Crimes.
